nodes.title: Darth Vader
nodes.content: The chosen one. Brought balance to the force. Before me thousands of Jedi, only two Sith. After me, two Jedi and two Sith. That's what you call balanced.

nodes.title: Emperor Palpatine
nodes.content: This is the Dark Lord of the Sith

nodes.title: Luke Skywalker
nodes.content: This is the Galaxy's only hope.

nodes.title: Leia Organa
nodes.content: This is the girl who is always counted out but comes up bg.

nodes.title: Obi-Wan Kenobi
nodes.content: Why did you try it Anakin? I had the high ground. And I've used that exact trick on Darth Maul which I must have told you about. Did you think I wouldn't see that shit coming? Come on young padawan.

nodes.title: Greedo
nodes.content: The green guy who was just too slow for Han Solo. Or was I innacurate? Did I shoot or not? Idk George Lucas keeps editing my only scene

nodes.title: Yoda
nodes.content: That baby me am not. Look nothing like him, I did. More handsome I am.

nodes.title: Boba Fett
nodes.content: Still being digested to this day in The Great Pit of Carkoon

nodes.title: Jabba The Hutt
nodes.content: Me want solo on my wall.

nodes.title: Lando Calrissian
nodes.content: I'm in it for the money, and the women, and the greater good, but definitely the money.
